# =============================================================================
# /root/ncn-workspace/.gitignore  —  workspace-wide ignores
# =============================================================================
# This is a monorepo for two products that are deployed independently:
#
#   core-console/   admin.example.com (ncn-api on deploy-host)
#   webmail/        mail.example.com  (ncn-mail on pop-03)
#
# Both ship via deploy/deploy.sh inside their own directory. The top-level
# deploy-all.sh chains them.
#
# Patterns below use **/ leading-globs so they apply at any depth — covers
# both projects without per-project duplicate .gitignores.

# ── Node / Vite frontend artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.vite/
**/build/

# ── Go build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/backend/ncn-api
**/backend/ncn-mail
**/backend/*.test
**/backend/__debug_bin*

# ── Editor / OS noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.tmp

# ── Local environment / secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Real secrets live in /etc/ncn-*/, never in the workspace. These rules
# defend against accidental dotenv-style files that might appear during dev.
**/.env
**/.env.*
*.local
**/secret*.local
**/*.key.local

# ── Claude Code per-project memory + settings ──────────────────────────────
# This directory contains conversation memory, slash-command snippets, and
# user preferences. Not part of the deployable product — keep out of the
# repo so it doesn't leak between machines.
**/.claude/

# ── Logs / temp ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
**/tmp/

# ── Local backups / compiled CLI binaries ──────────────────────────────────
# backups/ holds ad-hoc tar+age snapshots from scripts/backup-secrets.sh.
# Each clone snapshots its own state; the .tar.gz form has no value to
# other machines (and we don't want encrypted blobs in git either).
backups/
**/*.tar.gz

# cli/ncn-login/ncn-login is the compiled login CLI (ARM64 ELF on this
# box, x86 elsewhere). Source lives in cli/ncn-login/*.go; the binary
# itself is a per-machine build artifact, not source-of-truth.
cli/ncn-login/ncn-login
